"title": "5196: voice",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5196: voice",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The organ of speech; someone's voice expresses a person's character, thoughts and emotions, and attracts attention by its tone and volume.</p>\n<h2>The human voice</h2>\n<h3>The sound of familiar voices</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:14\">ACT 12:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:22\">GEN 27:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:3\">JDG 18:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:16\">1SA 24:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:17\">1SA 26:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:14\">SNG 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song8:13\">SNG 8:13</a></p>\n<h3>Groups of people speaking in unison</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:3\">EXO 24:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:24\">1SA 10:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:13\">2CH 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr23:11\">2CH 23:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:12\">EZR 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:22\">ACT 12:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:34\">ACT 19:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:22\">ACT 22:22</a></p>\n<h2>Voices communicate in various ways</h2>\n<h3>Voices expressing defiance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:8\">1SA 17:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:22\">2KI 19:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:23\">ISA 37:23</a></p>\n<h3>Voices that give a battle cry</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:20\">1SA 17:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr13:15\">2CH 13:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:9\">ISA 8:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:16\">JER 4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:19\">JER 4:19</a></p>\n<h3>Festive voices</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:35\">2SA 19:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:34\">JER 7:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:9\">JER 16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:10\">JER 25:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:11\">JER 33:11</a></p>\n<h3>Voices expressing distress</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg21:2\">JDG 21:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:34\">GEN 27:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:1\">NUM 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:7\">2SA 22:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:6\">PSA 18:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:36\">1KI 22:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:31\">JER 4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:30\">EZK 27:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:20\">DAN 6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:18\">MAT 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:15\">JER 31:15</a></p>\n<h2>Voices of varying volume</h2>\n<h3>God's loud voice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:5\">JOB 37:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:22\">DEU 5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:3\">ISA 33:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:2\">EZK 43:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:28-John12:29\">JHN 12:28–12:29</a></p>\n<h3>Loud human voices</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:12\">1SA 28:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:19\">2CH 20:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:12\">EZR 10:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:9\">ISA 40:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:33\">LUK 4:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:57\">ACT 7:57</a></p>\n<h3>God's quiet voice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:12-1Kgs19:13\">1KI 19:12–19:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job26:14\">JOB 26:14</a></p>\n<h3>Quiet human voices</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:16\">JOB 4:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:17\">ECC 9:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:2\">ISA 42:2</a></p>\n<h2>Voices addressed to God</h2>\n<h3>In praise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:15\">LUK 17:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:11\">JDG 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:55\">1KI 8:55</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:11\">EZR 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:1\">PSA 47:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:1-Ps100:4\">PSA 100:1–100:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:14\">ISA 24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:37\">LUK 19:37</a></p>\n<h3>In prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:7\">PSA 27:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:7\">DEU 33:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:1\">PSA 64:1</a></p>\n<h3>Assurance that God hears his people's voice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:3\">PSA 5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:23\">EXO 22:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:15\">DEU 24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:17\">PSA 55:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:20\">ISA 19:20</a></p>\n<h3>God's response to his people's voice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:9\">NEH 9:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:17\">GEN 21:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:23-Exod2:25\">EXO 2:23–2:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:9\">EXO 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:16\">NUM 20:16</a></p>\n<h3>God sometimes refuses to hear his people's voice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:18\">EZK 8:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:15\">ISA 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:1-Isa59:2\">ISA 59:1–59:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:12\">JER 14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:23\">AMO 5:23</a></p>\n<h2>The futility of lifting up one's voice to an idol</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg10:14\">JDG 10:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:26\">1KI 18:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:28\">1KI 18:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:12\">JER 11:12</a></p>\n<h2>Voices that proclaim God's word</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:18\">ROM 10:18</a></strong> <em>The original sense of the voice of the heavens is reapplied to all who proclaim the gospel.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:1\">ISA 58:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:8\">MIC 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:14\">ACT 2:14</a></p>\n<h2>The voice of God</h2>\n<h3>God's voice addresses individuals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:9\">GEN 3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:4\">EXO 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:4\">1SA 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:8\">ISA 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:4\">JER 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:28\">EZK 1:28</a></p>\n<h3>God's voice is awe-inspiring</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:3-Ps29:9\">PSA 29:3–29:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:26\">DEU 5:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:16\">DEU 18:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:2\">JOB 37:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:6\">PSA 46:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:33\">PSA 68:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:30-Isa30:31\">ISA 30:30–30:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:13\">ISA 42:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:24\">EZK 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:19\">HEB 12:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:26\">HEB 12:26</a></p>\n<h3>God's voice demands obedience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:26\">EXO 15:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:20\">DEU 30:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:22\">1SA 15:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:21\">ISA 30:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:7-Heb3:8\">HEB 3:7–3:8</a></p>\n<h3>God's voice affirms his Son</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:17\">MAT 3:17</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:11\">MRK 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:22\">LUK 3:22</a> <em>at Jesus Christ's baptism</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5\">MAT 17:5</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:7\">MRK 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:35-Luke9:36\">LUK 9:35–9:36</a> <em>at the transfiguration</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:28\">JHN 12:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:17-2Pet1:18\">2PE 1:17–1:18</a></p>\n<h2>The voice of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>His voice is recognisable</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:1-John10:5\">JHN 10:1–10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:14-John10:16\">JHN 10:14–10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:27\">JHN 10:27</a></p>\n<h3>His voice calls people to him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:37\">JHN 7:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:4-Acts9:7\">ACT 9:4–9:7</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:7-Acts22:9\">ACT 22:7–22:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:14-Acts26:16\">ACT 26:14–26:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:20\">REV 3:20</a></p>\n<h3>His voice raises the dead</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:25\">JHN 5:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:28\">JHN 5:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:43\">JHN 11:43</a></p>\n<h3>His voice cries out</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:46\">MAT 27:46</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:34\">MRK 15:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:50\">MAT 27:50</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:46\">LUK 23:46</a></p>\n<h2>Other voices</h2>\n<h3>The voices of angels</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:7\">JOB 38:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:6\">DAN 10:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:20-Matt1:21\">MAT 1:20–1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:13\">MAT 2:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:2\">REV 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:11-Rev5:12\">REV 5:11–5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:7-Rev14:9\">REV 14:7–14:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:2\">REV 18:2</a></p>\n<h3>The voice of wisdom</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:20\">PRO 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:1-Prov8:4\">PRO 8:1–8:4</a></p>\n<h3>The voices of the natural world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1-Ps19:4\">PSA 19:1–19:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:41\">JOB 38:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps93:3\">PSA 93:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:18\">ROM 10:18</a></p>",
